Name: KNG_SNCARC
Abstract:
King County, Washington arc features from the King County street network coverage. Covers also portions of Snohomish and Pierce Counties.  

The source coverage was derived from the King County Street Network coverage (kcsn). All feature classes other than arcs have been dropped and items have been removed from the AAT. Scale: 1:24,000.
